            <h1>Create a car</h1>
            <p class="desc lead">
                To create and offer your car for sale, use this API endpoint.
            </p>
            <p class="request post">
                POST /api/autos
            </p>
            <p class="request_body">
            <div>The request body should be car details (without the ID)</div>
<pre>{
        "brand": "opel",
        "name": "Opel Calibra A BJ 4/92 automatik",
        "price": 1250,
        "year": 1995,
        "damage": "",
        "last_seen": "2016-05-07T14:58:46",
        "image": "http://www...."
}</pre>

            </p>
            <p class="response_formats">
                Response formats: <span>JSON</span>, <span>CSV</span>
            </p>
